Module org.apache.jena.querybuilder

Package org.apache.jena.arq.querybuilder.handlers

package org.apache.jena.arq.querybuilder.handlers
Classes that implement SPARQL clauses but do not return instances of the builder. These classes are used by the various Builder implementations to consistently implement the various clauses. In most cases users of the Query Builder module will not need to manipulate these directly.
